ar     = 2019\n| next_title    = \n| next_year     = \n| misc          = \n}}\n\n\"'''Take Yourself Home'''\" is a song by Australian singer-songwriter [[Troye Sivan]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.idolator.com/7908395/troye-sivan-announces-new-single-take-yourself-home|title=Troye Sivan Announces New Single \"TAKE YOURSELF HOME\"|date=23 March 2020|website=[[Idolator (website)|Idolator]]|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/culture/133617/troye-sivan-announces-release-of-comeback-single-take-yourself-home/|title=Troye Sivan announces release of comeback single Take Yourself Home|date=31 March 2020|website=[[Gay Times]]|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref> The song was released via [[EMI Music Australia]] on 1 April 2020 as the lead single from his upcoming third studio album.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/news/pride/9340584/troye-sivan-announces-take-yourself-home-fans-react|title=Troye Sivan Announces &#39;Take Yourself Home&#39;: Fans React|date=2020-03-23|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://attitude.co.uk/article/troye-sivan-announces-new-single-take-yourself-home/23075/|title=Troye Sivan announces new single 'Take Yourself Home' and it's the good news we need right now|date=23 March 2020|website=[[Attitude.co.uk]]|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://vman.com/article/troye-sivan-is-releasing-a-new-single-take-yourself-home/|title=Out Today: \"Take Yourself Home\" by Troye Sivan {{!}} V Man|website=[[VMan]]|accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2020)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand Hot Singles ([[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4845|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=13 April 2020|